ppy and sometimes does a strange fast forward. Remember that DVD Architect Studio is system intensive and relies heavily on your video card. If your video card is not up to date, you will experience similar problems."]},"id":"936931a5-37fe-43d3-a334-b7f034712a77","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"fb52e9db-4253-4d32-bf8b-76156c906d69","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Sony&#39;s DVD Architect Studio is not for people with little patience. It is incredibly powerful DVD making software for those who know what they are doing. The inexperienced, however, will quickly want to throw their computers out of a window after trying to operate this DVD maker for the first time."]},"id":"2b9d58ea-c68f-4e4b-b8b9-891f91249ed1","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_2673","url":"/sony-dvd-architect-studio-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"j-d-chadwick","url":"/author/j-d-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"J.D. Chadwick","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"Q2hDFnLxcyQrSWYJF8ZLKH","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2008-10-29T21:34:52Z","datePublished":"2008-10-29T21:34:52Z","name":"Sony DVD Architect Studio","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about DVD Authoring Software here. Sony is a big name in multimedia software.","review":{"rating":43,"verdict":"There are many features, but DVD Architect Studio isn&#039;t an application you can learn on the fly.","pros":["There is comprehensive support to help you learn how to use the features."],"cons":["This application has a steep learning curve initially."]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out 